org.apache.juddi.v3.client.mapping

Class MapUDDIv2Tov3

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juddi.v3.client.mapping.MapUDDIv2Tov3

  • public class MapUDDIv2Tov3
extends Object
    Converts UDDIv2 objects to UDDI v3 objects. Note: these functions do not take into account the differences in key naming conventions. The good news is that UDDIv3 has backwards compatibility with v2.
    Author:
    Alex O'Ree
